{"tid":1589704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族新屋嶺扣留中心導賞團（第二回）","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:12:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d6fec4fdb595c223fbd56658960b0bbe776371","tid":1589704,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"日期：2019年9月26日（星期四）<br />\n時間：下午2:00-5:00<br />\n集合地點：九龍塘地鐵站D出口（地面位置集合），請提早15分鐘到達點名。<br />\n解散地點：九龍塘地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n當日活動：<br />\n- 在扣留中心正門介紹新居嶺扣留中心的前世今生、<br />\n- 講述811恐怖囚室的事件、<br />\n- 驅車前往小山崗俯看扣留中心全貌。<br />\n<br />\n費用：全免<br />\n名額：60人<br />\n<br />\n⚠️報名方法：必須在專頁內pm管理員，如接納參加導賞團會另行通知，參加者請自行衡量活動風險！<br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️特別注意<br />\n不接受即場參加！<br />\n<br />\n⚠️優先參與人士：<br />\n立法會議員<br />\n記者<br />\n銀髪族<br />\n其他人士<br />\n<br />\n如時間和集合地點有更改，會個別通知。<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m2WE42\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m2WE42&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=0264616b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m2WE42</a>"},{"pid":"72951ea252d140a30e1737460d24f37255fbc7ae","tid":1589704,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"eb0e67af0e08d082d766eac3e75c00da8a2c8502","tid":1589704,"uid":278391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"銀髮族好波，可惜開工參加唔到"},{"pid":"cf6590bd6ea2b8195e8a7715add51b288c42ffd2","tid":1589704,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"太平坤士呢"},{"pid":"2aeb193824967bcd062fbaf8b6b42d03174cbe46","tid":1589704,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2a6bd6d21a75f73261a237f16c2c3e40edbfcd","tid":1589704,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳<br />\n<br />\n五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccfeae1dd683a28403ebe0156a2b4592cf5a3b51","tid":1589704,"uid":300139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"願一切平安"},{"pid":"1367a21378be4cd2987ed629cf767c3a44ffc373","tid":1589704,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72951ea252d140a30e1737460d24f37255fbc7ae","tid":1589704,"uid":47605,"like":